<p>_ is based on &quot;Foundation Missed Connections&quot; by &quot;Toadking07&quot;: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-foundation-gripe-sheet">http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-foundation-gripe-sheet</a></p>
</blockquote>

